Write a one-time Node.js script called fix-emails-sent.js that reads all documents 
from Firestore collection 'users' and adds an emailsSent field to each one if it doesn't exist:

emailsSent: {
  day1: false,
  day3: false,
  day12: false,
  day14: false,
  reactivation: false
}

Use Firebase Admin SDK. Run with: node fix-emails-sent.js

